<p>Before opening:</p>

<ul>
  <li><a href="https://github.com/twbs/bootstrap/issues?utf8=%E2%9C%93&amp;q=is%3Aissue">Search for duplicate or closed issues</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://html5.validator.nu/">Validate</a> any HTML to avoid common problems</li>
  <li>Read the <a href="https://github.com/twbs/bootstrap/blob/v4-dev/.github/CONTRIBUTING.md">contributing guidelines</a></li>
</ul>

<p>Bug reports must include:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Operating system and version (Windows, macOS, Android, iOS)</li>
  <li>Browser and version (Chrome, Firefox, Safari, Internet Explorer, Microsoft Edge, Opera, Android Browser)</li>
  <li>A <a href="https://css-tricks.com/reduced-test-cases/">reduced test case</a> or suggested fix using <a href="https://codepen.io/">CodePen</a> or <a href="https://jsbin.com/">JS Bin</a></li>
</ul>
